    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Local Restrictions Support Grants (LRSG) and Additional Restrictions Grant (ARG): guidance for local authorities
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This guidance for local authorities is on paying grants to support businesses during the November to December 2020 national lockdown and periods of local restrictions.</p>

  </div>
</div>

