      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
    
          <div class="govspeak">
<h3 id="local-restrictions-support-grant-lrsg-schemes">Local Restrictions Support Grant (<abbr title="Local Restrictions Support Grant">LRSG</abbr>) schemes</h3>

<p>These schemes are to support local businesses during the national lockdown 5 November to 2 December 2020 and during periods of local restrictions.</p>

<p>The guidance is for use by local authorities and sets out the eligibility criteria, operation and delivery details for each <abbr title="Local Restrictions Support Grant">LRSG</abbr> strand.</p>

<h3 id="additional-restrictions-grant-arg-scheme">Additional Restrictions Grant (<abbr title="Additional Restrictions Grant">ARG</abbr>) scheme</h3>

<p>The Additional Restrictions Grant (<abbr title="Additional Restrictions Grant">ARG</abbr>) is funding for local authorities to support businesses in their local economies.</p>

<p>The guidance is for use by local authorities and sets out the eligibility criteria, operation and delivery details of the <abbr title="Additional Restrictions Grant">ARG</abbr> grant funding.</p>

</div>

</div>
      </section>
